T*
(Worked Example 1) Tj
T*
(1. Start with an example based on a simple classroom example involving Modern Physics.) Tj
T*
(2. Identify the exact idea in the main ideas and methods involved in Modern Physics that) Tj
T*
(the question is testing.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct method for Modern Physics step by step without skipping reasoning.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the final answer and explain why it is correct.) Tj
